          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);background:var(--success-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.3rem;flex-shrink:0;">&#x1F4DD;</div>
            <div style="flex:1;min-width:0;">
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px;">
                <span style="font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--gray-800);">Mind-Muscle Connection for Glutes</span>
                <span class="badge badge-green" style="font-size:.65rem;">Personal Note</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Discovered that squeezing at the top of hip thrust for 1-2s makes a huge difference in activation. Also, wider stance on abduction machine targets upper glutes better.</div>
              <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <span class="badge badge-blue" style="font-size:.65rem;">Hip Thrust</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue" style="font-size:.65rem;">Hip Abduction</span>
                <span class="badge badge-gray" style="font-size:.65rem;">Glutes</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-xs text-muted mt-1">Added Mar 22, 2026</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:14px;cursor:pointer;" onclick="showToast('Opening resource...')">
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.3rem;flex-shrink:0;">&#x1F4F0;</div>
            <div style="flex:1;min-width:0;">
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px;">
                <span style="font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--gray-800);">Protein Timing Doesn't Matter (Much)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-gray" style="font-size:.65rem;">Article</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Stronger By Science — Total daily protein intake matters far more than timing. The "anabolic window" is overblown. Just hit your daily target.</div>
              <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <span class="badge badge-gray" style="font-size:.65rem;">Nutrition</span>
                <span class="badge badge-gray" style="font-size:.65rem;">Protein</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-xs text-muted mt-1">Added Mar 18, 2026</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:14px;cursor:pointer;" onclick="showToast('Opening resource...')">
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);background:var(--danger-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.3rem;flex-shrink:0;">&#x1F3AC;</div>
