                <span class="badge badge-red" style="font-size:.65rem;">YouTube</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Renaissance Periodization — Key cue: "pull elbows to hips, not hands to chest." Changed my lat pulldown form completely.</div>
